"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/905559","Ministry of Defence","false","2018-05-21","<p>HMS Ocean was sold for £84 million, with £55 million of the revenue generated being reinvested in Defence - prior to the sale £29 million was spent on refitting to make her ready for sale.</p>","Aberconwy","Guto Bebb",,"2018-05-21T15:37:12.273Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/905559/answer","Biography information for Guto Bebb","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/905559/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/905559/answer",,,,,"11","Defence","Defence","2018-05-16","HMS Ocean","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Defence, what the cost to the public purse of the refit of HMS Ocean was; and what revenue was generated for his Department's budget from the sale of that vessel.","false","Biography information for Nia Griffith","Llanelli","Nia Griffith","144865"
"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/905560","Department for Transport","false","2018-05-21","<p>It is expected that the Task and Finish Group will submit its report for ministers to consider next month. The report will be published in due course.</p><p> </p><p>While the Department is eager to receive the report it is vital that the independently chaired group is granted the time it deems necessary to hear evidence, consider the issues and evaluate proposals to address these.</p>","Wealden","Ms Nusrat Ghani",,"2018-05-21T10:49:55.677Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/905560/answer","Biography information for Ms Nusrat Ghani","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/905560/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/905560/answer",,,,,"27","Transport","Transport","2018-05-16","Taxis: Licensing","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Transport, pursuant to the Answers of 24 April, 23 April, 28 March, 26 February, 29 January, 24 January, 22 January, 18 January, 8 January 2018 and 6 December 2017 to Questions 136807, 136288, 134056, 127728,  123767, 123012, 122413, 122522, 120771 and 116150 and with reference to the Answer of 12 February 2018 to Question HL5304, what the timetable is for the Task and Finish Group on Taxi and Private Hire Vehicles licensing to (a) submit and (b) publish its report; and what the reasons are for the time taken for that group to submit and publish its report.","false","Biography information for Wes Streeting","Ilford North","Wes Streeting","144959"
